{"tid":2270093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［最大贏家］習近平：延遲宣布建成小康、不訂GDP目標","createTime":"2020-11-04T01:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T02:31:08.000Z","uid":38744,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c07739f83aad52e38606b58aa53c4f6b53bb42e5","tid":2270093,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2732480903563045/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2732480903563045%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcypuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2294d1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2732480903563045/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【習近平：GDP翻一番做得到  外部環境複雜才不訂】<br />\n<br />\n事隔一個周末，官方公布了十四五規劃和2035年遠景目標全文，並附帶了總書記習近平在會上的說明稿。<br />\n<br />\n今次規劃其中令人意外的地方，是沒有明確具體經濟目標。習近平透露，在徵求意見時，一些地方政府和部門都建議訂出GDP翻一番的目標。<span class=\"red\">他指，從經濟發展能力和條件看，中國經濟有希望做到，但由於外部環境不明朗，所以只是訂出一個宏觀目標代替。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國本來計劃在今年全面脫貧和建成小康社會，習近平指目標<ins><strong>可以如期實現</strong></ins>，但由於仍在進行中，所以決定等到明年上半年，才正式宣布中國全面建成小康社會。</span>"},{"pid":"580a744b3c79add8093192bbb7c719ad17ab6364","tid":2270093,"uid":29188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29VtZZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29VtZZP.jpg&h=1e3b2334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sze24ry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsze24ry.jpg&h=8fbe928b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dfc661e73b1762f574c994dfcb8bae17d61d699","tid":2270093,"uid":145928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"580a744b3c79add8093192bbb7c719ad17ab6364","tid":2270093,"uid":29188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29VtZZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i